Inherit the Viper (2020). Genres: Crime, Drama. Cast: Josh Hartnett, Margarita Levieva, Chandler Riggs, Bruce Dern, Owen Teague. Inherit the Viper is a 2019 American crime drama film directed by Anthony Jerjen, in his feature directorial debut, from a screenplay by Andrew Crabtree. It stars Josh Hartnett, Margarita Levieva, Chandler Riggs, Bruce Dern, Valorie Curry, Owen Teague, and Dash Mihok.tan